Package com.ideas.snakesnladders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    State
    State Interface for the various states of the GameEngine
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configuration
    A Configuration object is responsible for stating Number of Rows on the Board.
    Configuration.Builder  
    Constants
    A Constant object contains hard-coded values for different constant items.
    DynamicGame
    A Snakes & Ladders game that can be configured based on the Configuration object.
    Game
    The heart of the Snakes and Ladders game.
    GameEngine
    A GameEngine object is the controller of the Snakes and Ladders game, defining its flow and outcome.
    RunningState
    State object that represents the running state of the GameEngine.
    SetupState
    State object that represents the configuration state of the GameEngine.
    StartState
    State object that represents the starting of the GameEngine.
    StaticGame
    A Snakes & Ladders game that runs on a predefined board setup using the StaticBoardBuilder and two players
    StopState
    State object that represents the stop state of the GameEngine.
